      dns_ip_added, dns_ip_removed_healthy and dns_ip_removed_failed
      for tracking DNS lookup response changes
    * Improve cloudi_service_health_check logging level use

2022-08-31 Michael Truog   <mjtruog at protonmail dot com>

    * Add cloudi_availability as a module for usage in internal
      CloudI services (previously was named cloudi_core_i_status)
    * Add the cloudi_core header files cloudi_availability.hrl and
      cloudi_constants.hrl for usage in internal CloudI services
    * Improve cloudi_service_health_check functionality
        * Allow failed TCP IPs to expire when they are missing from
          a valid DNS lookup response
        * Add tcp_test function for request/response testing
        * Improve configuration and hosts information

