    * Add linux_setcap.sh script for non-root Linux installations

2022-08-22 Michael Truog   <mjtruog at protonmail dot com>

    * Add size_erlang value to the CloudI Service API services_status output

2022-08-20 Michael Truog   <mjtruog at protonmail dot com>

