2021-06-13 Michael Truog   <mjtruog at protonmail dot com>

    * Change the ATS CloudI API subscribe function to use the
      ATS v2 function$name implement template idiom to automatically
      create the c_callback function used by the C CloudI API
      (now only the ATS callback function is necessary for the subscribe)
        * Added the subscribe$function function which must be implemented
          before calling the subscribe function
        * Removed the callback_attach function (made it private)

